{"tid":839554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 委員會建議最低工資調高至37.5元","createTime":"2018-09-28T04:33:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T02:19:19.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"992aa58b020332d3b1a979deb21f0f750504417d","tid":839554,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T04:33:01.000Z","msg":"Now新聞台】消息透露，最低工資委員會就調整最低工資水平達成共識，時薪由34.5元增至37.5元，增幅是8.7%。委員會下月底前向行政長官會同行政會議提交報告，若獲得通過，新水平明年五月一日生效。<br />\n<br />\n消息透露，最低工資委員會就調整法定最低工資水平達成共識，建議由現時的時薪34.5元加3元至37.5元，增幅達百分之8.7。是自2011年實施最低工資以來，四次調整最低工資中加幅最高的一次。<br />\n<br />\n根據統計處數字，如果最低工資加至37.5元，會有15萬6千多名僱員受惠。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，委員會早前舉行兩次全日會議，期間勞資雙方一度在37元及37.5元五毫子之間拉鋸，最終就37.5元「拍板」。委員會將會再開會討論有關報告並簽名作實。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=321827&amp;home=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D321827%26home%3D1&d=35VR44aBLSg6O01mXEyuI%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=73d42381\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D321827%26home%3D1&h=2d1b6081\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=321827&amp;home=1</a>"},{"pid":"ae124b7c5441f7720d445640447346074c2a2bf2","tid":839554,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T04:33:54.000Z","msg":"$50個tea 不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c5ea84e7606f7081006cf2dc250662799f9fd08","tid":839554,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T04:35:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"750e6970800326632447421244529e6991c0c819","tid":839554,"uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T04:38:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/19/133811_1d9fcb4f63a440a77c32deb42756910e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservi